# No secrets are required to run the scraper/extraction pipeline or the
# static dashboard locally. Firestore + the Cloud Run backend were dropped
# (Phase E) in favor of a static dashboard fetching pipeline-published
# JSON directly — there's no live backend or database left to configure.
#
# The one credential the project still needs — a Firebase Hosting deploy
# token for the scheduled publish step — is never stored in a file at all.
# See pipeline/orchestration_prompt.md for how it's provisioned.
